{"id":1108420,"global_id":"Z2lkOi8vaGFja2Vyb25lL1JlcG9ydC8xMTA4NDIw","url":"https://hackerone.com/reports/1108420","title":"HTML Injection on \"polls\" app - comments section (possibly XSS)","state":"Closed","substate":"resolved","severity_rating":"low","readable_substate":"Resolved","created_at":"2021-02-21T20:27:44.639Z","submitted_at":"2021-02-21T20:27:44.707Z","is_member_of_team?":false,"is_organization_group_member?":false,"is_triager?":false,"reporter":{"disabled":false,"username":"supr4s","url":"/supr4s","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/cnms4l7faunf0sht0ox61ouwsqlj/20fc426031f09e5347054871ae4e3af2478fd2b3d5e8a321468ecf6f2da5ac20"},"is_me?":false,"cleared":false,"verified":true,"hackerone_triager":false,"hacker_mediation":false},"team":{"id":13291,"url":"https://hackerone.com/nextcloud","handle":"nextcloud","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/hsgut1vi1cv8housqai9cm9383yx/235acf2ba808c3a51a94888fb977392c26f8fb0ccf77a81a4546c5e4065c06f1","medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/hsgut1vi1cv8housqai9cm9383yx/3f1ab5c6a9b6dadada1e6c8121700b884388bd0a43471fee1897a38ce57d0b2c"},"permissions":[],"submission_state":"open","default_currency":"usd","awards_miles":false,"offers_bounties":false,"state":"public_mode","only_cleared_hackers":false,"pentest_feature_enabled?":false,"pentest_retesting_ends_at":null,"profile":{"name":"Nextcloud","twitter_handle":"nextclouders","website":"https://nextcloud.com","about":"Access, share and protect your files, calendars, contacts, communication \u0026 more at home and in your enterprise."}},"has_bounty?":false,"can_view_team":true,"can_view_report":true,"is_external_bug":false,"is_published":false,"is_participant":false,"has_collaborators":false,"submitted_by_team_member":false,"submitted_with_assistant":false,"stage":4,"public":true,"visibility":"full","cve_ids":[],"singular_disclosure_disabled":false,"disclosed_at":"2021-03-31T10:27:10.651Z","bug_reporter_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2021-03-31T10:27:10.594Z","team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2021-03-31T10:11:38.540Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"Hi everyone,\n\nOn latest version of Polls app (1.7.5), I noticed a lack of user input filtering for the \"Description\" part of the survey. An HTML injection is therefore possible. I tried to inject JavaScript code to get an XSS but I didn't succeed. Certainly someone better than me will be able to do it.\n\n## Phishing\n\nKnowing that you can inject HTML, you can do cool stuff like phishing with the following code : \n\n```\n\u003cbr/\u003e \u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cmarquee\u003e\u003cp style=\"color:red;\"\u003e\u003cb\u003e!!!!! IMPORTANT message from Nextcloud administrator !!!!!!\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/marquee\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e A security issue was found last night.\u003cbr/\u003e \u003cp style=\"color:green;\"\u003ePlease go to manually on \u003ca\u003e\u003cb\u003echanging-password.cloud.evil.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/b\u003e to reset your password.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cb\u003e\u003cp style=\"color:red;\"\u003eThank you in advance for doing so as soon as possible. \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003ci\u003eThe IT team.\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e \u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e \u003cb\u003e\u003cmarquee\u003e\u003cp style=\"color:red;\"\u003e!!!!! IMPORTANT message from Nextcloud administrator !!!!!!\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/marquee\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e \u003cbr/\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\n```\n\nAnd the website changing-password.cloud.evil.com would first ask for entering the user's current password, before he enters his new password =\u003e password retrieved from the attacker's server\n\n**Proof-of-concept :** https://███/apps/polls/s/cxXkCK9LRXIKu5Oq\n\n\n\n## DoS (client side)\n\nYou can also make the user's PC spit by loading an infinite number of iframes. \n\n**Proof-of-concept (Warning, may crash your PC) :** https://███████/apps/polls/s/WKGKWHEFSSvPsHyC\n\n## Impact\n\n- Attract the user to redirect him to a malicious page and steal his personal identifiers\n- Client-side DoS\n- And many other things are possible by injecting HTML code at will and without filtering\n\nIn my opinion, I don't think it's a good thing to let the user add HTML code as he wants without being worried!\n\nRegards,\nSupras","weakness":{"id":60,"name":"Cross-site Scripting (XSS) - Generic"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":1204542,"file_name":"HTMLi_1.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/aqv7hs09dgbdmc61lypmjz3yhk2f?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22HTMLi_1.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27HTMLi_1.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQTKRGR5DQ%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T082602Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECcaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQCjeLxypZ5G09j46VFXMW3qEsv0oaHQnbg0Nzz963RZEwIhAPv4B3RET%2FPO7LFAgkBXtspEAAgafVXG8U%2BeYZmrPCcFKroFCPD%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQAxoMMDEzNjE5Mjc0ODQ5IgwkBk4kcdVDifPG2jcqjgUYfwjPeqykR8%2Bgakyaeaw7G6qDMVXfBpWAiFNlJxiE0IEMpc6ZF0gJ2xORmyjykf39ZF2TWq2f7vNCq7MHLNT%2BlHH8%2FA8bgXP2IdjTFiXVf6jJVXh%2Bpjv4yHCk%2Fa0rnNWfFjJ7NJCcjUuTc3927BCSUQqK9%2BybnS5ubHKUq2iw%2Fcu7rdLezh6godur1cfIx9q5Dd2VwDWUSYDyIAx6dVvw%2Fhv8so1tWCOb9B%2Bkm3CKIBiFmW5tOYTaZ5EqepbIsmS6IpNdSZvQ6sjDFlCwdgr80LVmqtPdh2ZEQsNpVyt8tDkU%2BBTvFPKj%2FQ7x9cYJM1oHCPOKCYKZTQz7%2FSRakdWdvR3Q93w7HoKTSdC3%2FLvSKHQ%2F9jKbGZS9%2BEAnU0pn1DhYX7YFE4RMpenz%2BTSnViDI2DY0w%2BaLkg2Hp1P9KYSNAr5FjK5u6ie8Fp8k6jsDg